 Sorry, this is getting too complex.

2:41:46.680 --> 2:41:49.680
 Well, it's a good way to estimate the amount of oxygen.

2:41:49.680 --> 2:41:54.680
 If you calculate the amount of oxygen based on the assumption that all this carbon 12 that's being taken out

2:41:54.680 --> 2:41:58.680
