2:42:05.680 --> 2:42:09.680
 So it's kind of a paradox and the only way to explain this paradox,

2:42:09.680 --> 2:42:14.680
 just on mass balance of how much stuff is in the air, how much stuff is in the oceans and so on,

2:42:14.680 --> 2:42:19.680
 is to assume that what oxygen was not the oxygen, it was sulfate.

2:42:19.680 --> 2:42:21.680
