 In one way, I think why it matters is that my expectation, I suppose, is that we will be over the next 100 years or so if we survive at all, that AI will increasingly dominate.

2:52:53.680 --> 2:53:03.680
 And pretty much anything that we put out into space going looking for other, well, for the universe for what's out there will be AI won't be won't be us.

2:53:03.680 --> 2:53:06.680
